Electronic Valve Control with Feedback(voltage is variable here)

 Developed a closed-loop simulation model of an electronically controlled valve system using Simscape integrated with Simulink control blocks
 Implemented a feedback control mechanism where system output is continuously fed back to regulate the input voltage
 Utilized a PI controller to adjust system response and maintain desired operating conditions
Modelled interaction between electrical input, control logic, and physical valve behaviour
 Analysed dynamic system response using scope outputs to study stability and control performance
